      "value": "When `ext:type-inheritance` is declared, `Package.dependencyRefs` must include a `Reference` for every Type in the transitive closure of base Types for any Type in `Package.types[]`. If `mode === \"bundled\"`, all such base Types must be present in `types[]`."
